column5: [(u'Brooklyn Lager Can', u'Hoppy Amber Red Lager - Brooklyn, NY - 5.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Brooklyn Lager is amber-gold in color and displays a firm malt center supported by a refreshing bitterness and floral hop aroma. Caramel malts show in the finish.', u'$6.00'), (u'Bud Light Lemonade Lager Can', u'Lager \u2013 Houston, Texas \u2013 4.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Made with real lemonade, this refreshingly crisp beer with a citrus twist has a delicious balance of tart and sweet, perfect for easy-drinking occasions under the sun.', u'$5.00'), (u'Coney Island Mermaid Pilsner Can', u'German Style Pilsner - Coney Island, NY - 5.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Mermaid Pilsner is a light-bodied, crisp drinking, nicely hopped lager. A heavy-handed addition of rye malt adds a mild spiciness, which is balanced by a light, fruity, floral hop aroma.', u'$6.00'), (u'Coney Island Merman IPA Can', u'IPA - Coney Island, NY - 5.8% ABV - 12oz Can - Huge melon, orange and kiwi flavors, and tropical aromas dominate, but are complemented by a strong melanoidin malt backing, finishing clean with the classic K\xf6lsch \u201csnap.\u201d', u'$6.00'), (u'Glutenberg IPA Can', u'Gluten Free IPA - Montreal, CA - 6% ABV - 16oz Can - Aromatic nose full of citrus, lemon and floral notes, a crisp and sharp mouthfeel paired with light caramel and hoppy flavors. A flavorful, very flavorful quencher.', u'$9.00'), (u'Ithaca Flower Power IPA Bottle', u'American IPA - Ithaca, NY - 7.2% ABV - 12oz Bottle - Enjoy the clover honey hue and tropical nose of our celebrated flagship ale. Flower Power is simultaneously punchy and soothing with a big body and a finish that boasts pineapple and grapefruit. ... The hint of apricot gives this beer a pleasant nose and fruity finish.', u'$7.00'), (u'Michelob Ultra Pure Gold Organic Can', u'Lager \u2013 St. Louis, MO \u2013 4.2% ABV - 12oz Can - A great tasting golden lager, with lower calories than ULTRA, signature low carbs, and a clean, balanced finish. Pure Gold is brewed with organic rice and barley malt, elevating the quality of the beer while delivering a superior taste.', u'$5.00'), (u'Miller High Life Lager Bottle', u'American Adjunct Lager - Milwaukee, WI - 4.6% ABV - 7oz Bottle - A classic American-style lager recognized for its consistently crisp, smooth taste and iconic clear-glass bottle. Miller High Life embraces its rich heritage and is known by its drinkers as an authentic, unpretentious beer.', u'$3.00'), (u'Modelo Especial Pilsner 16oz Can', u'Pilsner - Mexico - 4.4% ABV - 16oz Can - This rich, full-flavored Pilsner-style Lager delivers a crisp, refreshing taste. Well-balanced taste and light hop character with a crisp, clean finish. Modelo Especial is characterized by an orange blossom honey aroma with a hint of herb.', u'$6.00'), (u'Ommegang Witte Bottle', u'Orange Peel & Coriander Wheat Ale - Cooperstown, NY - 5.2% ABV - 16oz Bottle - It is pale straw in color, slightly hazy from the yeast, and topped with a huge white, fluffy head. Witte is pleasantly light on the tongue, balanced between malt and wheat sweetness. Hops and spice with a subtle clove note backed by flavors of lemon and sweet orange give way to a dry, crisp, refreshing finish.', u'$6.00'), (u'Original Sin Black Widow Cider Can', u'Blackberry Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - The black widow is fruit-forward, yet tart, with a tantalizing complexity, made with blackberries and freshly pressed New York apples.', u'$6.00'), (u'Original Sin Hard Cider Can', u'Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - Traditional cider that contains no artificial flavors or colors. Very pale in color (like an un-oaked chardonnay). Nicely carbonated, with a good dose of apple crispness and buttery apple pulp.', u'$6.00'), (u'Pabst Blue Ribbon Lager 16oz Can', u'American Adjunct Lager - Milwaukee, TN - 4.6% ABV - 16oz Can - Brewed with a combination of 2 & 6-row malted barley, select cereal grains and American and European hops, Pabst Blue Ribbon is fermented with a proprietary lager yeast. Our unique fermentation and maturation process results in a smooth, full bodied beer with a clean, crisp finish with a fine noble hop aroma.', u'$4.00'), (u'Peak Organic Fresh Cut Pilsner Can', u'Bohemian Pilsner - Portland, ME - 4.6% ABV - 12oz Can - Fresh Cut is a dry-hopped pilsner. Chinook, Citra and Centennial hops provide aromas of citrus, grass and spice. Though the front palate is loud with IPA qualities, the finish is distinctly pilsner- crisp, dry and extremely refreshing.', u'$6.00'), (u'Peak Organic IPA Can', u"American IPA - Portland, ME - 7.1%ABV - 12oz Can - This unique India Pale Ale features our favorite hops\u2014Simcoe, Amarillo and Nugget. A generous Amarillo and Simcoe dry hop provide for an assertive, hop-forward nose and front palate. We don't use traditional bittering hops in our IPA, providing nothing but stimulating citrus and floral characteristics.", u'$6.00'), (u"Samuel Smith's Nut Brown Ale Bottle", u'Nut Brown Ale \u2013 England, UK \u2013 5% ABV - 12oz Bottle - It pours a rich mahogany brown color, with a solid beige head that shows good retention. The bouquet opens with enticing aromas of toasted malts, brown bread, caramelized brown sugar and warm hazelnuts. The medium-weight body is full and creamy in feel, with pleasant toasted nut and caramel malt flavors.', u'$8.00'), (u'Sixpoint Bengali IPA Can', u'IPA \u2013 Brooklyn, New York \u2013 6.6% ABV - 12oz Can - The enhanced Sixpoint IPA formulation, first released in the summer of 2014 and uses a blend of new hop strains for a juicy, citrusy, piney hop slashing. It all started with an epic video game marathon back in 2004. Rocking blaze-orange homebrew, we saw the foam rings down the glass like tiger stripes. Thousands of batches and tweaks later, the BENGALI\xae still slashes. Tip in back and let gravity do the work. Game on!', u'$7.00'), (u'Sixpoint Resin IIPA Can', u"Double IPA - Brooklyn, NY - 9.1% ABV - 12oz Can - We remember our first sip of hoppy beer, do you? Nearly spit that $#!^ out. Now we fantasize about this stuff. Thinking about those hop ones...bursting with juice...ripe as all hell...makes you look forward to that first RESIN\xae all day long. Can't wait.", u'$7.00'), (u'Truly Hard Seltzer Can', u'Passion Fruit, Mango, Pineapple, Watermelon Kiwi - 5% ABV - 12oz Can - Made with simple ingredients and hints of our favorite fruits. Never made with artificial sweeteners or flavors.', u'$5.00'), (u'Wild Basin Hard Seltzer Can', u'Yumberry, Blueberry Mango, Black Raspberry and Strawberry Coconut - Wild Basin, CO - 5% ABV - 12oz Can - We exist to keep you running wild and free from the barriers that get in the way of reaching your destination. To help you along the way, we\u2019re bringing the natural and flavorful bounty of the Wild Basin to you \u2013 invigorating your adventurous spirit.', u'$5.00'), (u"Wolffer's Cider Bottle", u'Dry Rose Cider - Sagaponack, NY - 6.9% ABV - 10oz Bottle - Bright shiny rose in color. Fantastic fresh floral notes fill the glass; the Crispin aromas especially stand out with fine hints of yeast. The mouth-feel is pure and clean, with a nice balance of sweet fruit, elegant acidity and fine tannins that provide a long and pleasant finish.', u'$11.00'), (u'Yuengling Lager 16oz Can', u"Traditional American Lager - Pottsville, PA - 4.4% ABV - 16oz Can - Yuengling\xae Traditional Lager is famous for its rich amber color, medium-bodied flavor and distinct character. It's brewed with roasted caramel malt for a subtle sweetness and a combination of cluster and cascade hops.", u'$5.00'), (u'Kung Fu Girl Pinot Grigio Can', u'Columbia Valley, WA - 2018 - 12.5% ABV - 12oz Can - Kung Fu Girl Pinot Grigio is a vibrant dry white wine with shimmering aromas and flavors of bright citrus and white peach, in a portable and easily chillable can. With a light body and a crisp finish, this table white wine is ideal for pairing with white pizza, fresh seafood, and pork. For best quality, chill this crisp white wine in the refrigerator for two to two and a half hours before serving at about 50 degrees.', u'$13.00'), (u'Bananajama', u'rum, organic coconut ice cream, hemp milk, organic banana, organic strawberry preserves, organic graham crackers', u'$14.00'), (u'Boozy Be My Shake', u'organic ice cream, organic milk or hemp milk and your choice of spirit! please choose 1 spirit. we will only honor your first selection.', u'$14.00'), (u'Cocoacrush', u"whiskey, organic chocolate ice cream, hemp milk, organic chocolate sauce, organic newman's chocolate cookies", u'$14.00'), (u'On The Rocks Aviation', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - A throwback to the era when airplanes were brand new. This classic gin cocktail, The Aviation, is crafted with Larios London Dry Gin, and flavors of dry cherry, lemon, and violet.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Cosmopolitan', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - A wildly popular cocktail, The Cosmopolitan is a simple cocktail with a big history. Often referred to as \u2018the cosmo\u2019 this cocktail blends Effen vodka, flavors of cranberry, triple sec, lemon zest, and lime.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Jalapeno Pineapple Margarita', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - The perfect drink for those who share our love of all things hot. The Jalape\xf1o Pineapple Margarita uses a flavor combination of pineapple and triple sec married with plata Tres Generaciones tequila and the heat from the jalape\xf1o.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Mai Tai', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - As the old tiki adage goes, \u2018what one rum can\u2019t do, three rums can\u2019. We blend Cruzan light and dark rums and combine our unique blend with flavors of orange, pineapple, orgeat, and coconut for the perfect Mai Tai.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Margarita', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - One of the most recognizable and sought after cocktails in the world, The Margarita offers a perfect balance between tequila, tart lime flavors and triple sec. Yes please. Enjoy a glass of your favorite rose wine with these adorable gummy bears infused with real rose from provence.', u'$9.95'), (u'Champagne Fruttini', u"Pop the bubbly, there's a new way to enjoy your Champagne! These juicy, tiny fruit gems are infused with the finest Champagne and sprinkled with superfine sugar crystals. All-natural and vegan, their refreshing bubbly taste will put you in the party mood. Pop one into a glass of Champagne for a little touch of sweetness!", u'$9.95'), (u'Sparkling Ros\xe9 Bears', u'Get sparkling with these grown-up gummy bears infused with ros\xe9 wine and dusted in tart sugar crystals.', u'$9.95'), (u'Italian Lemon Fruttini', u"If you love p\xe2te de fruit, you'll really love their beautiful Italian cousins. These juicy, tiny fruit gems are infused with the sweet nectar of fresh femminello lemons. This intensely-aromatic lemon variety is grown in Italy and used to make Italian limoncello, a lemon liqueur. Each soft bite is rolled in extra-fine Italian sugar crystals for a taste that's sweet, tart, and completely divine. 100% all-natural.", u'$9.95'), (u'Strawberry Daiquiri Hearts', u'Daydreaming of a daiquiri? These heart-shaped daiquiri gummies with fresh strawberry flavor and a twist of lime are the perfect sweet (with a touch of tart) treat. Just one juicy bite and you\u2019ll be transported poolside, sipping on the fruity frozen concoction \u2014 tiny cocktail umbrella not included.', u'$9.95'), (u'Maple Bourbon Caramels', u'Made with top-shelf bourbon, these smooth caramels have just the right amount of kick.', u'$9.95'), (u"Robin's Egg Caramels", u'A rich and creamy caramel egg is coated in premium dark chocolate and dipped in a delicate candy shell.', u'$9.95'), (u"Marshmallow S'Mores", u'A mini marshmallow is drenched in milk chocolate, then rolled in crushed graham crackers.', u'$9.95'), (u'Martini Olive Almonds', u'No olives here, just smartly-dressed white chocolate-covered almonds masquerading as cocktail garnishes.', u'$9.95'), (u'Dark Chocolate Toffee Almonds', u'Fresh California almonds are candied with a pinch of sea salt, then dipped in rich dark chocolate.', u'$9.95'), (u'Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramels', u'Rich & creamy caramels are dipped in superfine dark chocolate, with just a kiss of sea salt.', u'$9.95'), (u'Birthday Cake Caramels', u'Make every day your birthday with these celebratory birthday cake caramels rolled in tiny rainbow sprinkles.', u'$9.95'), (u'Chocolate Covered Cookie Dough-Small Cube', u'Get a taste of your grandma\u2019s freshly mixed cookies with these chewy chocolate chip cookie dough bites. Dunked in dark chocolate and rolled in walnuts, this indulgent treat will have you back for more. Made in the USA.', u'$9.95'), (u'Choco Chip Cookie Chocolate Bar', u'It doesn\u2019t get better than this. Bite into this creamy milk and dark chocolate bar blend topped with chocolate chip cookie dough, dark chocolate chips, and crunchy walnuts for the ultimate treat you won\u2019t want to share.', u'$9.95'), (u'Sugar-Free Dark Chocolate Almonds', u"Giving up sugar doesn't have to be bittersweet. You'll love these fresh-roasted California almonds dipped in premium sugar-free dark chocolate. It's the perfect treat to satisfy a candy craving but without the sugar. Because chocolate makes everything better.", u'$9.95'), (u'Fuji Apple Caramel', u'Crisp Fuji apple flavor is paired with smooth, rich caramel for a mouthwatering taste sensation. These perfectly-sized caramel bites are sweet upfront and tart on the finish. Our most refreshing caramel yet.', u'$9.95'), (u'Sugar Cookies', u'A teeny tiny sugar cookie is dipped in white chocolate, then sprinkled with superfine sugar.', u'$9.95'), (u'Tequila Cordials', u'Tequila and chocolate-need we say more. Our Casamigos tequila cordial features a sphere of rich dark chocolate filled with a smooth sip of Casamigos A\xf1ejo tequila. Take a shot and see what the buzz is all about.', u'$9.95'), (u'Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Cashews', u'Plump roasted cashews are dipped in premium dark chocolate with a light sprinkling of sea salt.', u'$9.95'), (u'Sugarfina Pearls Pink', u'Tiny milk chocolate droplets are coated in a delicate sugar shell, in dazzling sugarfina hues.', u'$9.95'), (u'Kona Espresso Beans', u'The finest hand-picked Kona beans from Hawaii are dipped in exquisite dark chocolate. These all-natural espresso beans will have you addicted in the most delectable way. Get ready for a delicious buzz...', u'$9.95'), (u'Hawaiian Sea Salt Macadamia Nuts', u'Plump roasted macadamia nuts are dipped in rich dark chocolate and sprinkled with Hawaiian sea salt.', u'$9.95'), (u'Dark Chocolate Marshmallow Eggs', u'A fluffy vanilla marshmallow is dipped in rich dark chocolate and a crunchy candy shell', u'$9.95'), (u'Mint Chocolate Caviar', u'Delicate, sweet and chic, these tiny peppermint pearls are dipped in rich dark chocolate.', u'$9.95'), (u'Pink Sparkle Pops', u'Crunchy pink chocolates are filled with strawberry-flavored popping candy. These tasty poppy candy chocolates are tasty treats that pack quite the punch with a sweet burst of sparkle and pop in every bite. Sweet, pink, and sparkling - these are a few of our favorite things!', u'$9.95'), (u'Aphrodite Strawberry', u'Candied Greek strawberries are dipped in sumptuous milk chocolate, then dressed in a speckled sugar shell. These exotic treats are named after the Greek Goddess Aphrodite, who, according to Greek myth, created the strawberry when she wept heart-shaped tears of sadness for her love, Adonis.', u'$9.95'), (u'Golden Truffle Eggs', u'A creamy milk chocolate truffle is infused with hazelnut and vanilla, then dipped in a shimmery golden shell.', u'$9.95'), (u'Peanut Butter Milkshake', u"Before peanut butter met jelly, he had a major thing going on with chocolate. And no wonder. The two of them together are a match made in malt ball heaven. These exquisite malt balls elevate PB&C to new heights. Light and crispy malt centers are dipped in creamy peanut butter, then covered in the finest milk chocolate. Better stock up, you'll go totally nuts for them.", u'$9.95'), (u'Limoncello Cordials', u'A white chocolate shell holds a tiny shot of limoncello, an Italian liqueur made from fresh sweet lemons. CONTAINS ALCOHOL: Max 2.5% alcohol by weight/volume. It is unlawful to sell or give to persons who are under the legal drinking age. Women who are pregnant or may become pregnant should not consume this product.', u'$9.95'), (u'Pumpkin Pie Caramels', u"A bite-sized slice of heaven. We're totally obsessed with these savory, fresh-from-the-oven caramels. Close your eyes and you'll swear it's a miniature version of your mom's award-winning pumpkin pie (only better... sorry mom). A soft, smooth caramel is surrounded by sweet pumpkin white chocolate, infused with delicate notes of cinnamon, nutmeg, cardamom and allspice. One bite and you'll be whisked away to pumpkin paradise.", u'$9.95'), (u'Chocolate Confetti', u"It's a party in your mouth with these tiny drops of creamy milk chocolate in a colorful candy shell. These pastel rainbow milk chocolate candies pair perfectly with our Birthday Cake Caramels and Ice Cream Cones for a sweet birthday treat.", u'$9.95'), (u'Sparkle Pops', u'These crunchy chocolates are filled with popping candy for a big burst of sparkle and pop.', u'$9.95'), (u'Peach Bellini\xae', u'These all-natural gummies are filled with juicy peach nectar, then dusted in sweet and sour crystals.', u'$22.00'), (u'Champagne Bears\xae', u'Infused with bubbly Dom P\xe9rignon, these sophisticated bears sparkle in flavors of brut and ros\xe9.', u'$22.00'), (u'Bubbly Bears', u'Champagne Bears with a sour twist. Our classic Champagne-infused gummy bears are dusted in sweet and tart sugar crystals for a sophisticated taste that really pops. Made with Dom P\xe9rignon Vintage Champagne. A Sugarfina exclusive. Non-alcoholic.', u'$22.00'), (u'But First Ros\xe9', u'With an infusion of ros\xe9 wine from Provence in every bite, our newest rosette-shaped gummies are the perfect treat for any ros\xe9 lover.', u'$22.00'), (u'Sugar Lips\xae', u'Pucker up to these sweet & sour gummy lips in delicious flavors of watermelon, berry & bubble gum.', u'$22.00'), (u'Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramels', u'Rich & creamy caramels are dipped in superfine dark chocolate, with just a kiss of sea salt.', u'$22.00'), (u'Boutique Tasting Box Collection', u'Welcome to the ultimate gourmet tasting experience. Modeled after the signature Candy Wall in our Sugarfina boutiques, this unique tasting box is the perfect way to discover your new favorite flavors or gift an over-the-top taste of the sweet life. We're on a mission to quench your thirst for more.", u'$3.00'), (u'Brooklyn Lager Can', u'Hoppy Amber Red Lager - Brooklyn, NY - 5.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Brooklyn Lager is amber-gold in color and displays a firm malt center supported by a refreshing bitterness and floral hop aroma. Caramel malts show in the finish.', u'$5.00'), (u'Coney Island Mermaid Pilsner Can', u'German Style Pilsner - Coney Island, NY - 5.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Mermaid Pilsner is a light-bodied, crisp drinking, nicely hopped lager. A heavy-handed addition of rye malt adds a mild spiciness, which is balanced by a light, fruity, floral hop aroma.', u'$5.00'), (u'Coney Island Merman IPA Can', u'IPA - Coney Island, NY - 5.8% ABV - 12oz Can - Huge melon, orange and kiwi flavors, and tropical aromas dominate, but are complemented by a strong melanoidin malt backing, finishing clean with the classic K\xf6lsch \u201csnap.\u201d', u'$5.00'), (u'Glutenberg IPA Can', u'Gluten Free IPA - Montreal, CA - 6% ABV - 16oz Can - Aromatic nose full of citrus, lemon and floral notes, a crisp and sharp mouthfeel paired with light caramel and hoppy flavors. A flavorful, very flavorful quencher.', u'$8.00'), (u'Ithaca Flower Power IPA Bottle', u'American IPA - Ithaca, NY - 7.2% ABV - 12oz Bottle - Enjoy the clover honey hue and tropical nose of our celebrated flagship ale. Flower Power is simultaneously punchy and soothing with a big body and a finish that boasts pineapple and grapefruit. ... The hint of apricot gives this beer a pleasant nose and fruity finish.', u'$6.00'), (u'Kelso Nut Brown Lager Can', u'German Dunkel Style Lager - Brooklyn, NY - 5.6% ABV - 12oz Can - On the nose: woodsy, herbal, with a bit of black dirt and a minty top note. On the palate, very lightly toasty with the barest notes of milk chocolate. European flavor hops. Clean, but soft bitterness. A bit of a green, woody note at the end.', u'$5.00'), (u'Miller High Life Lager Bottle', u'American Adjunct Lager - Milwaukee, WI - 4.6% ABV - 7oz Bottle - A classic American-style lager recognized for its consistently crisp, smooth taste and iconic clear-glass bottle. Miller High Life embraces its rich heritage and is known by its drinkers as an authentic, unpretentious beer.', u'$3.00'), (u'Ommegang Witte Bottle', u'Orange Peel & Coriander Wheat Ale - Cooperstown, NY - 5.2% ABV - 16oz Bottle - It is pale straw in color, slightly hazy from the yeast, and topped with a huge white, fluffy head. Witte is pleasantly light on the tongue, balanced between malt and wheat sweetness. Hops and spice with a subtle clove note backed by flavors of lemon and sweet orange give way to a dry, crisp, refreshing finish.', u'$5.00'), (u'Original Sin Hard Cider Can', u'Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - Traditional cider that contains no artificial flavors or colors. Very pale in color (like an un-oaked chardonnay). Nicely carbonated, with a good dose of apple crispness and buttery apple pulp.', u'$5.00'), (u'Original Sin Black Widow Cider Can', u'Blackberry Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - The black widow is fruit-forward, yet tart, with a tantalizing complexity, made with blackberries and freshly pressed New York apples.', u'$6.00'), (u'Sixpoint Meltdown IPA Can', u'New England IPA - Brooklyn, NY - 8% ABV - 12oz Can - A lush, hazy, juicy IIPA with ripe tropical and bright citrus characteristics, and a soft, easy finish. Loaded up with enough dry-hops to melt your face. Brewed w/ Mosaic and Mandarina Bavaria Hops.', u'$6.00'), (u'Sixpoint Resin IIPA Can', u"Double IPA - Brooklyn, NY - 9.1% ABV - 12oz Can - We remember our first sip of hoppy beer, do you? Nearly spit that $#!^ out. Now we fantasize about this stuff. Thinking about those hop ones...bursting with juice...ripe as all hell...makes you look forward to that first RESIN\xae all day long. Can't wait.", u'$6.00'), (u'Truly Hard Seltzer Can', u'Passion Fruit, Mango, Pineapple, Watermelon Kiwi - 5% ABV - 12oz Can - Made with simple ingredients and hints of our favorite fruits. Never made with artificial sweeteners or flavors.', u'$4.00'), (u"Wolffer's Cider Bottle", u'Dry Rose Cider - Sagaponack, NY - 6.9% ABV - 10oz Bottle - Bright shiny rose in color. Fantastic fresh floral notes fill the glass; the Crispin aromas especially stand out with fine hints of yeast. The mouth-feel is pure and clean, with a nice balance of sweet fruit, elegant acidity and fine tannins that provide a long and pleasant finish.', u'$9.00'), (u'Band of Roses Rose Can', u'Columbia Valley, WA - 2018 - 12% ABV - 12 oz Can - Band Of Roses Rose is a dry blush wine with a silky palate and vibrant floral notes to enjoy with your latest playlist and serve to your favorite guest list. This rose wine has hints of crisp tangerine and a touch of passion fruit.', u'$13.00'), (u'Kung Fu Girl Pinot Grigio Can', u'Columbia Valley, WA - 2018 - 12.5% ABV - 12oz Can - Kung Fu Girl Pinot Grigio is a vibrant dry white wine with shimmering aromas and flavors of bright citrus and white peach, in a portable and easily chillable can. With a light body and a crisp finish, this table white wine is ideal for pairing with white pizza, fresh seafood, and pork. For best quality, chill this crisp white wine in the refrigerator for two to two and a half hours before serving at about 50 degrees.', u'$13.00'), (u'The Velvet Devil Red Blend Can', u'Columbia Valley, WA - 2016 - 13.5% ABV - 12oz Can - The Velvet Devil Red Blend Wine is a fresh and appealing blend, with flavors of pure velvet, black cherry and toasty oak - all in a conveniently portable can. Floral overtones and a polished core of currant combine with a full body and velvety finish for a wonderful pairing with burgers, steak fajitas and bacon. Chill this canned wine in the refrigerator for two hours before serving.', u'$13.00'), (u'Cucumber Gin Old Fashioned - Socialite', u'Brooklyn, NY - 28% ABV - 3.4 Oz Bottle - Gin leads with fresh cucumber and elderflower to back it up. Celery bitters round out this floral, botanical cocktail.', u'$8.00'), (u'Organic Vodka Pineapple Sling - FOMO', u'Brooklyn, NY - 20% ABV - 3.4 Oz Bottle - Pineapple and turmeric combine to create an earthy yet refreshing tropical profile, backed up with\x03a touch of heat from the flavorful Hatch Green Chile.', u'$8.00'), (u'Rose & Hops Gin Sling - Iron Lady', u'Brooklyn, NY - 20% ABV - 3.4 Oz Bottle - Rose and citrus provide a floral refreshing start, followed by the hops\u2019 delicate, bitter dry finish.', u'$8.00'), (u'On The Rocks Aviation', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - A throwback to the era when airplanes were brand new. This classic gin cocktail, The Aviation, is crafted with Larios London Dry Gin, and flavors of dry cherry, lemon, and violet.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Cosmopolitan', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - A wildly popular cocktail, The Cosmopolitan is a simple cocktail with a big history. Often referred to as \u2018the cosmo\u2019 this cocktail blends Effen vodka, flavors of cranberry, triple sec, lemon zest, and lime.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Jalapeno Pineapple Margarita', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - The perfect drink for those who share our love of all things hot. The Jalape\xf1o Pineapple Margarita uses a flavor combination of pineapple and triple sec married with plata Tres Generaciones tequila and the heat from the jalape\xf1o.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Margarita', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - One of the most recognizable and sought after cocktails in the world, The Margarita offers a perfect balance between tequila, tart lime flavors and triple sec. We set our margarita apart from the crowd with Hornitos\xae Plata Tequila.', ''), (u'On The Rocks Old Fashioned', u'Kentucky - 40 Proof - Staying true to the original recipe, we keep our Old Fashioned strong and simple using a generous pour of Knob Creek\xae Bourbon Whiskey, bitters, cane sugar, orange, cherry, and lemon zest.', '')]
